lead_paragraph: South Africa slid to 105 for six on the third day of the second and final test against New Zealand on Monday but were still firmly in command at Centurion, holding a 372-run lead.

headline.print_headline: South Africa in Complete Command in Pretoria
headline.main: South Africa in Complete Command in Pretoria
